description:
Amongst all the festivities and fun... here is the real meaning of Christmas! (in Lego)


Lego - The Birth of Jesus

chapters.title: do not be afraid to take Mary home as your wife
and you are to give him the name Jesus
While they were there, the time came for the baby to be born
She gave birth to her firstborn, a son
She wrapped him in cloths and placed him in a manger
because there was no room for them in the inn.
So they hurried off and found Mary and Joseph, and the baby
